WEBVTT

00:00.008 --> 00:02.359
- <i>Previously on "Gotham"...</i>
- SOFIA: Harvey is weak.

00:02.406 --> 00:04.139
And how many more cops need to die

00:04.175 --> 00:06.242
- because of his incompetence?
- GORDON: As of this moment,

00:06.297 --> 00:08.297
I'm assuming the captaincy
of Gotham Central.

00:08.332 --> 00:10.366
Nothing in Gotham is free.

00:10.401 --> 00:12.501
You wanted a gangster
to help you get rid of Penguin.

00:12.537 --> 00:14.804
This is what that help looks like.

00:14.839 --> 00:17.873
PYG: The whole town
has gone hog wild for the Pyg.

00:17.909 --> 00:19.208
(snorts)

00:19.243 --> 00:20.810
GORDON: Turns out that Pyg's real name

00:20.845 --> 00:22.745
- is Lazlo Valentine.
- (alarm bell ringing)

00:22.780 --> 00:24.480
And he just escaped.

00:24.515 --> 00:26.382
THOMPKINS: I haven't been looking
for a cure for your brain, Ed,

00:26.417 --> 00:28.050
because I was afraid
that if I told you the truth,

00:28.085 --> 00:29.952
you would go back
to being who you were before.

00:29.987 --> 00:31.954
And I like who you've become.

00:31.989 --> 00:34.290
BRUCE: I'm not the hero Gotham needs.

00:34.325 --> 00:35.324
I took the dark path.

00:35.359 --> 00:36.792
ALFRED: Yes, you did.

00:36.828 --> 00:38.961
And it's gonna be
a long, bumpy journey back.

00:38.996 --> 00:40.129
What...?

00:40.164 --> 00:41.297
Hello, Victor.

00:41.332 --> 00:42.398
Where's the boy?

00:42.433 --> 00:44.066
SOFIA: Alive, for now.

00:44.101 --> 00:45.367
If Oswald wants to keep it that way,

00:45.403 --> 00:47.236
he will meet me
under the Crown Point Bridge.

00:50.374 --> 00:52.374
OSWALD: You wanted a war,

00:52.410 --> 00:54.743
you've got one!

00:55.817 --> 00:58.184
We will wait for Mr. Cobblepot

00:58.219 --> 01:00.820
to send instructions.

