01:14.335 --> 01:15.935
Hello.

01:20.220 --> 01:23.220
Where is Penguin, little man?

01:25.513 --> 01:28.147
(guns cocking)

01:28.182 --> 01:30.182
♪ ♪

01:51.372 --> 01:52.972
(radio beeps)

01:53.007 --> 01:54.407
This is Gordon.

01:54.449 --> 01:56.316
I need forensics in West End Alley.

01:56.344 --> 01:58.911
Black market doc.

01:58.947 --> 02:00.646
Pyg was here.

02:00.682 --> 02:02.648
Looks like he got a new face.

02:02.684 --> 02:03.883
(coughing)

02:24.505 --> 02:28.107
So, Penguin's out building
support amongst the gangs.

02:28.142 --> 02:31.577
Pretty soon, every criminal in
Gotham is gonna be hunting us.

02:31.613 --> 02:34.513
He's out building support
because we made him look weak.

02:34.549 --> 02:37.750
We kill him, and all the gangs
will support me.

02:37.785 --> 02:39.952
I'm still a Falcone.

02:39.988 --> 02:42.989
Yeah, you mentioned that.
About a billion times.

02:43.024 --> 02:44.423
(door opens)

02:48.014 --> 02:49.829
(Tabitha sighs)

02:49.864 --> 02:51.964
He doesn't know where Penguin is.

02:52.000 --> 02:54.700
(phone vibrating)

02:54.736 --> 02:56.736
(sighs) What?

03:01.994 --> 03:04.377
I'll be right there.

03:04.412 --> 03:06.734
Was that about Penguin?

03:07.063 --> 03:08.714
No.

03:13.721 --> 03:15.421
Harper.

03:15.456 --> 03:17.356
We were an hour outside of Gotham

03:17.392 --> 03:18.824
when I got waylaid by Victor Zsasz.

03:18.860 --> 03:20.559
He took Sofia, gave me this.

03:20.595 --> 03:22.094
I woke up in Virginia.

03:22.130 --> 03:23.929
Damn it. I had a deal with Penguin.

03:23.965 --> 03:25.564
MAN: There's more. We're getting word

03:25.600 --> 03:27.566
Penguin had some meeting
under the Crown Point Bridge

03:27.602 --> 03:28.701
late last night.

03:28.736 --> 03:30.202
Gunfire, a car blown up.

03:30.238 --> 03:32.838
- Sofia Falcone was there.
- All right.

03:32.874 --> 03:34.540
We have to find Penguin. Harper?

03:34.575 --> 03:36.641
- I'm good, Cap.
- Put out a citywide BOLO.

03:36.696 --> 03:38.930
I'll find Sofia. What about the Pyg?

03:38.965 --> 03:40.577
I heard he escaped from Arkham.

03:40.602 --> 03:42.526
Tracked him to a black market surgeon.

03:42.586 --> 03:45.594
He's already got a new face.
Lazlo Valentine is gone.

03:45.649 --> 03:48.072
- But if we don't find him, what...
- Focus on the bigger problem.

03:48.769 --> 03:50.775
We've got a war to stop, people.

03:59.319 --> 04:02.086
So, you gonna tell us why
we're in your dad's house?

04:02.122 --> 04:04.122
Why do you think?

04:14.200 --> 04:15.800
Sofia.

04:20.173 --> 04:21.947
You look tired.

04:22.276 --> 04:25.143
Ms. Kean, it's good to see you again.

04:25.666 --> 04:27.578
Likewise.

04:27.614 --> 04:29.147
So, this is weird.

04:31.384 --> 04:33.284
Why are you here, Father?

04:33.319 --> 04:36.354
What did I tell you when you
asked to return to Gotham?

04:36.389 --> 04:37.488
I know...

04:37.524 --> 04:39.032
What did I tell you?!

04:40.878 --> 04:43.127
- That I wasn't ready.
- Exactly.

04:43.163 --> 04:45.667
And you came back anyway.

04:46.121 --> 04:48.299
Perhaps I should've acted then,

04:48.334 --> 04:51.068
but I was indulgent, curious.

04:51.457 --> 04:54.300
Who is this daughter I raised?

04:55.472 --> 04:57.859
Father, Penguin is weak.

04:57.929 --> 04:59.644
If you help me, we can end this.

04:59.679 --> 05:02.319
- I don't want Gotham.
- I don't believe that.

05:02.358 --> 05:04.148
You love this city.

05:04.184 --> 05:06.896
I used to, yes.

05:07.287 --> 05:09.255
But I'm dying, Sofia.

05:09.857 --> 05:11.896
Someone else can have Gotham.

05:12.028 --> 05:14.225
What I care about now is my family.

05:14.260 --> 05:15.393
And I am your family.

05:15.428 --> 05:17.161
And I want this. I deserve this.

05:17.197 --> 05:19.030
Gotham belongs to me.

05:22.735 --> 05:26.204
Your actions have disgraced our family.

05:26.239 --> 05:27.772
Tell me how sleeping with Jim Gordon,

05:27.807 --> 05:29.373
the man who killed your brother,

05:29.618 --> 05:31.774
helped reclaim Gotham.

05:32.070 --> 05:33.540
I'm sorry. What?

05:33.641 --> 05:36.347
I have done many things
I will have to answer for,

05:36.382 --> 05:39.108
but I always knew the meaning of honor.

05:39.960 --> 05:42.753
You have proven that you do not.

05:46.226 --> 05:48.135
Children.

05:48.494 --> 05:51.796
They can be such disappointments.

05:56.502 --> 05:59.070
I kill him, and this is over! Please.

05:59.563 --> 06:02.125
FALCONE: You know why
I came when Penguin called?

06:02.196 --> 06:04.575
It's because you were going to lose.

06:05.032 --> 06:07.612
If you were anyone but my daughter,

06:07.946 --> 06:10.749
you'd be dead right now.

